item.description: Hi, this is Robert Sheppard, owner and operator of rfs express, llc.  Rfs express is a hotshot service company that was founded in September of 2006 and is currently partnered with United Vision Logistics, located in Lafayette, LA.   Since our founding, I have traveled just under one million miles and have made over 2500 deliveries with no accidents or violations.
